## Limitations

This report is based on available data and literature up to October 2023. The healthcare landscape is dynamic, and new policies or market changes could alter the factors influencing healthcare costs. Additionally, while the report highlights major factors, it may not capture all nuances or regional variations in healthcare pricing. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive analysis.